	(text_box "Protection for USB-C\n- Electrostatic Discharge\n- Overvoltage and Power Protection\n	- polyfuse on vbus line\n- EMI filtering inline on D+/D-\n- USBLC6-2P6, IP4220CZ6,125\n\nProtection for Charger IC\n-\n\nProtection for Boost Converter\n-\n\n\n-----\nI placed EMI and ESD protection on my usb-c 2.0 D- and D+ lines in the form of USBLC6-2P6 and EXC14CE900U.\n\nDo I still need to add resistors or pull up these lines?\n\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 12.7 292.1 0)
